        "whyStudyIt": "To categorize organisms and understand evolutionary complexity.",
        "relationshipWithPrevious": "Expands on the 'unit' concept by showing diversity in structure.",
        "relationshipWithFuture": "Sets stage for DNA location studies later.",
        "keywords": [
          "Nucleus",
          "Membrane-bound",
          "Prokaryote",
          "Eukaryote"
        ],
        "teacherMoves": [
          "Use a 'House vs. Tent' analogy: Eukaryotes have rooms (organelles) and walls; Prokaryotes are open tents."
