          "Demonstrate 'Selective Permeability' with a sieve analogy."
        ],
        "examples": [
          "Onion skin cells have both membrane and wall.",
          "Cheek cells only have membrane."
        ],
        "visuals": [
          "Diagram showing fluid mosaic model (simplified)",
          "Comparison of Plant vs. Animal cell outer layers"
        ]
      }
