        "question": "Why did Robert Hooke name the structures he saw 'cells'?",
        "level": "Understanding",
        "expectedResponse": "They looked like small rooms or monk's cells.",
        "answerPoints": [
          "Mentioned resemblance to honeycomb/rooms",
          "Named after monks' quarters (Cellulae)"
